text: Yacouba Coulibaly (born 2 October 1994) is a Burkinabé professional footballer who plays as a left back for French club Le Havre and the Burkina Faso national team. ==Career== Born in Bobo-Dioulasso, Coulibaly has played for RC Bobo Dioulasso and Le Havre. He made his international debut in 2015, and was named in their squad for the 2017 Africa Cup of Nations. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Burkinabé footballers Category:Burkinabé expatriate footballers Category:Burkina Faso international footballers Category:RC Bobo Dioulasso players Category:Le Havre AC players Category:Paris FC players Category:Ligue 2 players Category:Championnat National 2 players Category:Championnat National 3 players Category:Association football fullbacks Category:2017 Africa Cup of Nations players Category:Burkinabé expatriate sportspeople in France Category:Expatriate footballers in France
